<h3 id="perugia">Perugia</h3>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Airport name:</strong> <em>Aeroporto Internazionale dell‚ÄôUmbria - Perugia ‚ÄúSan Francesco d‚ÄôAssisi‚Äù - S.A.S.E. SpA</em></li>
  <li><strong>Address:</strong> <em>Via dell‚Äôaeroporto snc, 06134 Perugia PG, Italy</em></li>
</ul>

<p>Flights from London <strong>Stansted</strong>.</p>

<p>To get to <strong>Siena</strong> you can either take:</p>

<ul>
  <li><em>Car</em>: Approx 1,20h</li>
  <li><em>Bus</em>: Approx 2,20h</li>
</ul>

