<ul>
  <li><strong>Address:</strong> <em>Agriturismo Podere Casato, SP484, 12, 53019 Castelnuovo Berardenga SI, Italy</em></li>
</ul>

<p>Directions from Siena to the venue can be found below. The journey takes approx. 25 mins by car.</p>

